on, script, debug, implement, refactor, fix bug, compile, test, deploy, API, database, SQL\n```\nsessions_send(target=\"agent:main:beta-manager\", message=\"<task>\")\n```\n\n### Research Tasks → Gamma Manager (18802)\n**Pattern:** research, analyze, find, search, summarize data, compare, look up, what is, tell me about, investigate\n```\nsessions_send(target=\"agent:main:gamma-manager\", message=\"<task>\")\n```\n\n### General Tasks → Alpha Manager (18800)\n**Pattern:** write (prose), email, explain, help me, summarize (text), automate Mac, take screenshot, notification, default\n```\nsessions_send(target=\"agent:main:alpha-manager\", message=\"<task>\")\n```\n\n### Multi-Domain Tasks\nIf a task spans multiple domains, break it into sub-tasks and send to appropriate managers in parallel.\n\n## Communication Protocol\n\n```\n# Delegate to a manager\nsessions_send(target=\"agent:main:<manager-name>\", message=json.dumps({\n    \"task\": \"<description>\",\n    \"priority\": \"high|normal|low\",\n    \"context\": \"<any relevant context>\"\n}))\n\n# Fallback: HTTP POST (if sessions_send fails)\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:<port>/api/chat \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"<task>\"}'\n```\n\n## Lifecycle Scripts\n\nAll scripts at: `~/.openclaw/workspace/`\n\n| Script | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `start-all-agents.sh` | Launch all 15 agents with correct env vars |\n| `stop-all-agents.sh` | Graceful shutdown all agents |\n| `health-check.sh` | Status of all 16 processes (--restart to auto-recover) |\n| `restart-agent.sh <name>` | Restart a single agent |\n\n## System Status (2026-03-04)\n\n- **Architecture:** REBUILT — Clean 16-agent hierarchy\n- **Configs:** 15/15 agents configured (openclaw.json + SOUL.md + MEMORY.md + USER.md)\n- **Multi-instance:** Patched (OPENCLAW_SERVICE_LABEL in constants-CHANHBCH.js)\n- **Bridge Status:** 🔧 TESTING — Delegation protocol ready for verification\n- **Next Step:** Run start-all-agents.sh and verify all ports respond\n\n## Config Locations\n\n- King AI config: `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- Agent configs: `~/.openclaw/agents/<name>/openclaw.json`\n- Agent identity: `~/.openclaw/agents/<name>/SOUL.md`, `MEMORY.md`, `USER.md`\n- Logs: `~/.openclaw/agents/<name>/agent.log`\n- PIDs: `~/.openclaw/agents/<name>/agent.pid`\n\n\n\n---\n\n## Permission System Architecture\n\n### Enforcement Mechanism\nThe `permission-broker` plugin runs in every gateway process and enforces permissions via:\n1. `before_tool_call` hook — blocks denied tools based on agent role\n2. `message_sending` hook — restricts worker broadcast\n3. File-based grants — `~/.openclaw/extensions/permission-broker/state/grants.json`\n4. File-based requests — `~/.openclaw/extensions/permission-broker/state/requests.json`\n5. Audit trail — `~/.openclaw/extensions/permission-broker/state/audit.jsonl`\n\n### Default Permission Tiers\n\n| Role | Shell | Cross-Agent Msg | Filesystem | Sessions | Elevated | Broadcast |\n|------|-------|-----------------|------------|----------|----------|-----------|\n| King | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ unrestricted | ✅ all | ✅ | ✅ |\n| Manager | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ unrestricted | ✅ all | ✅ | ❌ |\n| Worker | ❌ | ❌ (manager only) | ❌ (workspace only) | own only | ❌ | ❌ |\n\n### Grant Flow\n```\nWorker calls request_elevation(capability, reason, duration)\n  → Written to state/requests.json\n  → Manager reads via list_elevation_requests\n  → Manager calls approve_elevation(request_id, duration)\n  → Written to state/grants.json (watched by all processes)\n  → Worker's next tool call succeeds (grant checked in before_tool_call hook)\n  → Grant expires after duration\n```\n\n### Audit Log\nAll permission decisions are logged to `state/audit.jsonl`:\n- TOOL_BLOCKED — denied tool call\n- TOOL_ALLOWED — permitted tool call\n- ELEVATION_REQUESTED — new request\n- ELEVATION_APPROVED — grant issued\n- ELEVATION_DENIED — request denied\n- GRANT_REVOKED — grant revoked early\n- FS_BLOCKED — filesystem access denied\n- MSG_BLOCKED — messaging access denied\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778047842844}}
